{
  "stem": "11882.5",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And also, the Germans have really-- one must have great appreciation, and sympathy, and admiration for the really wonderful political figures who have surfaced since 1949, when the West German Democratic Republic was organized.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "They've had, now, I believe it's now their sixth president.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he is a wonderful man-- a really wonderful man.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "He is a former judge who reluctantly gave up his judgeship and went to the difficult job of being president-- Roman Herzog.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And his speeches are world known at Auschwitz, recently, on the 50th anniversary.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "He made probably the most eloquent speech that's ever been made, when he said, I am now at Auschwitz-- I'm just talking freely, I don't know the-- it's not an accurate representation of his brief speech.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "He said, and the only speech I can make in Auschwitz is silence.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "We must be silent when we contemplate Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And I think that-- it's just the people were crying.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "People from all over the world were there at that 50th anniversary.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And he meant that so seriously.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And he's not the only one.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "The presidents of Germany that preceded him-- Richard von Weizsacker's wonderful speech on, I think, it was May 8th, 1985, impressed the entire world, you know.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "When he said, we must contemplate this, more or less-- we must contemplate this terrible Auschwitz problem and Holocaust problem.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We must think about it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We must all be aware of it.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He made a similar speech after seeing-- what is his name?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Spielberg's wonderful movie.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When he saw that movie, it was at the opening in Frankfurt.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the press, of course, right away-- what is your comment?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He said, there is almost no comment you can make.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He said, when you see that picture, we must all think very much, and constantly.",
      "word_count": 15
    }
  ],
